n</reference>-->\r\n\r\n','default/modern','one_column',NULL,NULL,NULL),(3,'About Us','one_column',NULL,'Located in SoCal right at the heart of the Inland Empire, Kens Tool Supply has been supplying Riverside and the surrounding cities with great quality tools and supplies. Whether looking to buy or just researching your next tool, at Kens Tool Supply we strive to be that one stop destination for all things tools!!  ','about',NULL,'<div id=\"repairWrap\">\r\n<div id=\"repairLeft\">\r\n<div id=\"repairImage\"><img src=\"http://etoolsrus.net/new_site/images/about_us_image.png\" alt=\"Tool Repair Service at Ken\'s Tool Supply\" width=\"636\" height=\"249\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"repairKtsLogo\"><img src=\"http://etoolsrus.net/new_site/images/kts_logo_sm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"109\" height=\"84\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"repairBodyText\">\r\n<h1>About Ken\'s Tool Supply</h1>\r\n<p>Ken\'s Tool Supply houses a comprising selection of industry standard tools and equipment for the professional craftsman and the DIY enthusiast alike. With brands such as Bosch, Makita, Dewalt, Milwaukee, Porter Cable, Jet, Powermatic, Proto, Sioux, Norton, and many more. With brands like these, you\'re sure to find what you\'re looking for.<br /><br />At Ken\'s Tool Supply we service what we sell and even if we don\'t sell it, if its broken chances are we can fix it. Also, our manufacturer authorized repair department can warranty most top brands. Contact us for more details.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"line-separator1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"repairKtsLogo\"><img src=\"http://etoolsrus.net/new_site/images/kts_web_sm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"109\" height=\"84\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"repairBodyText\">\r\n<h2>Online Store</h2>\r\n<p>Need routine, scheduled maintenance or a major overhaul, when you need service on your power tool, Ken\'s Tool Supply offers a fast and dependable repair service.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Here\'s how it works:<br /> <br /> </strong>Drop your tool at your most conveniently location</p>\r\n<p><strong>Want &nbsp;an estimate before your tool is repaired?<br /> </strong>We will estimate your repair cost and will not proceed with the repairs without your approval<br /> <strong><br /> Is your tool still under warranty?&nbsp;<br /> </strong>Ken\'s Tool Supply is an Authorized repair center for most top brands</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"line-separator1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"repairKtsLogo\"><img src=\"http://etoolsrus.net/new_site/images/kts_store_sm.png\" alt=\"Ken\'s Tool Supply Store\" width=\"109\" height=\"84\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"repairBodyText\"><a name=\"#ktsstore\"></a>\r\n<h3>Riverside Store</h3>\r\n<p>For over 60 years Ken\'s has grown to become one of the largest suppliers <br /> of industrial quality tools and accessories in Southern California.</p>\r\n<p>We credit our success to a few principles:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dedication to outstanding customer service</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Knowledgeable sales staff</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Great prices and a great selection</strong><br /> <strong><br /> </strong></p>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msa=0&amp;msid=205247217133880748383.0004c844e8445083b99e1&amp;gl=us&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;t=m&amp;f=d&amp;daddr=Ken\'s+Tool+Supply+%4033.998205,-117.349029&amp;source=embed&amp;ll=34.045832,-117.342224&amp;spn=0.398263,0.686646&amp;z=10&amp;output=embed\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"500\" height=\"350\"></iframe><br /><small>View <a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-align: left;\" href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msa=0&amp;msid=205247217133880748383.0004c844e8445083b99e1&amp;gl=us&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;t=m&amp;f=d&amp;daddr=Ken\'s+Tool+Supply+%4033.998205,-117.349029&amp;source=embed&amp;ll=34.045832,-117.342224&amp;spn=0.398263,0.686646&amp;z=10\">Ken\'s Tool Supply</a> in a larger map</small></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"repairRight\">\r\n<div id=\"repairInfo\">\r\n<h4>Service Hotline</h4>\r\n<p>Have a tool, accessory, application or service question?<br /> <strong>Mon-Fri: 7am-6pm<br /></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"line-separator2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><strong></strong>Call us at 1-800-819-TOOL<br /> <strong>1-800-819-8665<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"line-separator2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><strong></strong>Contact us here</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"socialMedia\"><img src=\"http://etoolsrus.net/new_site/images/social_media.png\" alt=\"Social Media\" width=\"249\" height=\"59\" usemap=\"#media_Map\" border=\"0\" /> <map id=\"media_Map\" name=\"media_Map\"> \r\n<area shape=\"fb\" coords=\"1,3,58,58\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/Kens-Tool-Supply/168440519834820\" target=\"_blank\" />\r\n \r\n<area shape=\"yt\" coords=\"64,0,122,58\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" />\r\n \r\n<area shape=\"gp\" coords=\"127,0,186,58\" href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/b/115387501511044061048/115387501511044061048/posts\" target=\"_blank\" />\r\n \r\n<area shape=\"tw\" coords=\"191,0,248,58\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" />\r\n </map></div>\r\n<div id=\"repairLocations\">\r\n<h5>Service Locations</h5>\r\n<div class=\"line-separator2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>Riverside Location<br /> <strong>Ken\'s Tool Supply</strong><br /> 1751 Marlboriugh Avenue<br /> Riverside CA 92507<br /><strong>Mon-Fri: 7:30am-4:30pm</strong><br /> 951-686-2542 ext. 602<br /><br /></p>\r\n<div class=\"line-separator2\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>Montclair Location<br /> <strong>Tools-R-Us</strong><br /> 9055 Central Avenue<br /> Montclair CA 91762<br /><strong>Mon-Fri: 7am-6pm</strong> <br /> 909-626-9500 ext. 402</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2007-08-30 21:01:18','2013-03-19 07:22:22',1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4,'Customer Service','two_columns_right',NULL,NULL,'customer-service',NULL,'<div class=\"page-head\">\r\n<h3>Customer Service</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=\"disc\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n<li><a href=\"#answer1\">Shipping &amp; Delivery</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"#answer2\">P